headline: Palantir (PLTR) Could Be the Next Oracle, Says Wedbush in Bullish New Call

headline: 2 No-Brainer Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stocks to Buy in July
summary: Taiwan Semiconductor is one of the best stocks to profit from growing demand for chips needed for artificial intelligence.  Demand for Oracle's cloud infrastructure services is soaring, which is powering the stock to record highs.  Artificial intelligence (AI) is the next industrial revolution.
